{"tid":147040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗黑錢的真相","createTime":"2017-03-07T14:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T01:20:17.000Z","uid":75927,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"895dbca5b09c080425fb3c2aabcbedd68233edfa","tid":147040,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CHANWANHOI/posts/1429257120449751?notif_t=notify_me_page&amp;notif_id=1488869052397320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCHANWANHOI%2Fposts%2F1429257120449751%3Fnotif_t%3Dnotify_me_page%26notif_id%3D1488869052397320&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=918c8ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CHANWANHOI/posts/1429257120449751?notif_t=notify_me_page&amp;notif_id=1488869052397320</a><br />\n<br />\n轉自 雲海 陳雲海 Facebook page<br />\n<br />\n若果警務人員收受捐款，先要得到署方批准，並且有相關完善法例監管; 但係警務署已經證實，警務人員嘅家人親戚，係完全可以接受任何捐款以及唔需要得到批准亦都冇法律監管！咁即係話，黑社會可以捐錢俾警務人員嘅親戚，之後再由親戚畀返錢相關人士！呢啲洗黑錢方式係咪近乎完美？！"},{"pid":"3405aacf8ed3ff9c6403ab72f3e85b7ee796eeaa","tid":147040,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"香港警察除左做水馬重可以做埋洗衣機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真好使好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b2645708d72f9a82fc9ffa5e46cbbe2665b694","tid":147040,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90d7fd0647929b1752dd776c2994fec19a44033f","tid":147040,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"警黑一家！<br />\n<br />\n香港不愧為全球最有效率既國家級洗黑錢機器<br />\n有黑警幫手洗！<br />\n<br />\n我建議雲海報比FATF知:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fatf-gafi.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fatf-gafi.org&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=763b9bcf\" target=\"_blank\">www.fatf-gafi.o